	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=>RE: YET ANOTHER REPOST OF MY EXTREMELY LONG MAGICIAN GUIDE</a> <a id=fs8 href=#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Thu, Jun 21st 9:21 AM 2001</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>A couple of things to add:<br>It is SUICIDE to try to solo wisps at lvl 8 like Zuranthium implies you should do. You CAN take 1 wisp but it is wayyyy too easy to pull 2, and I still ahd trouble with 2 at lvl 11, though I usually won.<br>Wisps drop gls about every 10-15 wips, usually. If you're LUCKY you get 1 per 5. However, if you let your pet outdamage you than you kill 2 times the wisps to lvl, and 2x the wisps=2x the gls.<br>NEVER, EVER,EVER use rain of blades on wisp island. I tried once and 1 kerra spider wandered into the area of effect. Okay, 1 spider isn't too bad. That's when the other 4 showed up( <br>Don't waste your money on flme bolt. More often than not it's partially resisted and does less damage than shock of blades.<br>When you kill dwarf skellies, give the bone chips to Gunlock Jure in the pally guild. Some exp and faction.<br>At levels 8-10, try hunting in crushbone. It's MUCH less dangerous tahn wisps and CB belts sell for 1pp or so so you can sell them for great money.<br>That's all I can think of for now, I'll post again if I left something out )<br>Kranken, gnome mage of the 14th circle<br>EQ expet extrorinaire =P</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
